}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "YSM00A-1.6" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The FCC test report states that the P27AD1006D FCC ID covers the following models... *'''SerComm''' AD1006D (Dual antenna), AD1006S (Single antenna) *'''TRENDnet''' TEW-635BRM (doesn't seem to be) and TEW-657BRM (assumed) *'''unknown''' WL-358 and WL-359 *'''LevelOne''' WBR-6601 and WBR-6602
